
	Java Convention
		Class/Interface	-	PascalCase
		Method/Field	-	camelCase eg. nextInt()
		local/argument	-	lowercase
		constant		-	UPPERCASE
		package			-	lowercase
		keywords		-	lowercase
		
	Stream	-	Flow of data
		1. DataInputStream						java.io
		2. BufferedReader + InputStreamReader	java.io
		3. Scanner								java.util
		4. Console								java.io
		
	Deprecated	-	Outdated
	
	gets()	-	is dangerous and should not used.
	
	System is a class.
	out is field of System Class that is reference to an instance
	of PrintStream Class
	println/printf/print is a method defined in PrintStream class
	
	
